  {
    "_id": "article_scraper",
    "_body": "<h1 id=\"article-scraper\">Article Scraper</h1>\n<p><a\nhref=\"https://github.com/brombaut/article-scraper/actions/workflows/build_and_test.yml\"><img\nsrc=\"https://github.com/brombaut/article-scraper/actions/workflows/build_and_test.yml/badge.svg\"\nalt=\"CI\" /></a> <a\nhref=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/article_scraper\"><img\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/article_scraper\" alt=\"npm\" /></a> <a\nhref=\"https://app.codecov.io/gh/brombaut/article-scraper\"><img\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/brombaut/article-scraper\"\nalt=\"Codecov\" /></a></p>\n<p>Package for scraping information from different blogging\nwebsites.</p>\n<h3 id=\"currently-supported-sites\">\u2705 Currently supported sites</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://dev.to/\">dev.to</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"planned-sites-to-support\">\ud83d\udea7 Planned sites to support:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/\">medium.com</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://martinfowler.com/\">martinfowler.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"installing\">Installing</h2>\n<p>\n<p>For the latest version:</p>\n</p>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb1\"><pre\nclass=\"sourceCode bash\"><code class=\"sourceCode bash\"><span id=\"cb1-1\"><a href=\"#cb1-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"ex\">npm</span> i article_scraper</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb2\"><pre\nclass=\"sourceCode typescript\"><code class=\"sourceCode typescript\"><span id=\"cb2-1\"><a href=\"#cb2-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"im\">import</span> { ArticleMetaData<span class=\"op\">,</span> ArticleScraper } <span class=\"im\">from</span> <span class=\"st\">&quot;article_scraper&quot;</span><span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb2-2\"><a href=\"#cb2-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a></span>\n<span id=\"cb2-3\"><a href=\"#cb2-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">const</span> url <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"st\">&quot;https://dev.to/ashish9342/commenting-code-good-practices-3d23&quot;</span><span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb2-4\"><a href=\"#cb2-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">const</span> scraper<span class=\"op\">:</span> ArticleScraper <span class=\"op\">=</span> <span class=\"kw\">new</span> <span class=\"fu\">ArticleScraper</span>(url)<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb2-5\"><a href=\"#cb2-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">await</span> scraper<span class=\"op\">.</span><span class=\"fu\">scrape</span>()<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb2-6\"><a href=\"#cb2-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"kw\">const</span> result<span class=\"op\">:</span> ArticleMetaData <span class=\"op\">=</span> scraper<span class=\"op\">.</span><span class=\"fu\">articleMetaData</span>()<span class=\"op\">;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The <code>ArticleMetaData</code> result will contain information\nabout the article in the following format. Any errors encountered during\nscraping will be added to the <code>errors</code> attribute.</p>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb3\"><pre\nclass=\"sourceCode typescript\"><code class=\"sourceCode typescript\"><span id=\"cb3-1\"><a href=\"#cb3-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>ArticleMetaData {</span>\n<span id=\"cb3-2\"><a href=\"#cb3-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>  title<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;Commenting Code | Good Practices&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-3\"><a href=\"#cb3-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>  minuteRead<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"dv\">3</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-4\"><a href=\"#cb3-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>  tags<span class=\"op\">:</span> [</span>\n<span id=\"cb3-5\"><a href=\"#cb3-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    {</span>\n<span id=\"cb3-6\"><a href=\"#cb3-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      name<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;#programming&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-7\"><a href=\"#cb3-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      href<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;https://dev.to/t/programming&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-8\"><a href=\"#cb3-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      color<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;#ffffff&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-9\"><a href=\"#cb3-9\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      backgroundColor<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;#890606&#39;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-10\"><a href=\"#cb3-10\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    }<span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-11\"><a href=\"#cb3-11\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    {</span>\n<span id=\"cb3-12\"><a href=\"#cb3-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      name<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;#javascript&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-13\"><a href=\"#cb3-13\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      href<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;https://dev.to/t/javascript&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-14\"><a href=\"#cb3-14\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      color<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;#000000&#39;</span><span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-15\"><a href=\"#cb3-15\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>      backgroundColor<span class=\"op\">:</span> <span class=\"st\">&#39;#F7DF1E&#39;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-16\"><a href=\"#cb3-16\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    }<span class=\"op\">,</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb3-17\">